### Crear combination (pre-requisito)
# @name createCombination
POST http://localhost:3000/api/combinations
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "dateFrom": "2024-01-01T10:00:00Z",
  "dateTo": "2024-01-01T18:00:00Z",
  "lapsNumber": 50,
  "mandatoryStops": 2,
  "userType": "premium"
}

### ID de combination
@combinationId = {{createCombination.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener todas las races
GET http://localhost:3000/api/races

### Crear race
# @name createRace
POST http://localhost:3000/api/races
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "raceDateTime": "2024-01-15T14:00:00Z",
  "result": null,
  "description": "Argentina Grand Prix",
  "registrationDeadline": "2024-01-10T23:59:59Z",
  "combination": "1"
}

### ID de race
@id = {{createRace.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener race por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/races/1

### Actualizar race (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/races/2
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "description": "Argentina Grand Prix - Modified"
}

### Actualizar solo result (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/races/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "result": "1. Verstappen, 2. Hamilton, 3. Russell"
}

### Eliminar race
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/races/{{id}}